---
title: Tahini-Hoisin Turkey Noodles with Mixed Veggies and Peanuts
description: This Asian-inspired noodle dish gets its distinct flavour from tahini! That's right -- incorporating this nutty condiment gives the sauce a nutty aroma and a velvety mouthfeel.
